title: Ep. - 279 - CANDIACE DILLARD BASSETT FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF POTOMAC BIG BROTHER WITH ROB CESTERNINO
description:
Candiace Dillard Bassett from Bravo’s Real Housewives of Potomac talks about her life before the show, including growing up in a military family and working in politics, whether pageant contestants or other housewives are more cut throat, and what happens this season.

 

Rob Cesternino from Rob Has a Podcast helps Kate provide a review of CBS’ season 22 of Big Brother All Stars.
